Certainly! Here's a sample email template to inform your leads about the SonarQube notification threshold integration into the Jenkins build pipeline:

Subject: Important: SonarQube Notification Threshold Integration in Jenkins Build Pipeline

Dear [Lead's Name],

I hope this message finds you well. We're excited to inform you about an important enhancement to our development process that will significantly improve the quality of our code and streamline our workflow.

**What's Changing?**
We are integrating SonarQube's powerful code quality analysis and notification thresholds into our Jenkins build pipeline. This integration will allow us to:

- Continuously monitor and assess code quality.
- Automatically detect and flag issues, vulnerabilities, and code smells.
- Set customized notification thresholds to ensure code quality standards are met.
- Promptly address and prioritize issues to deliver higher-quality software.

**Why is this Important?**
Ensuring code quality is essential for the success of our projects. By integrating SonarQube's capabilities into our Jenkins build pipeline, we aim to enhance the reliability and maintainability of our software. This proactive approach will help us catch and resolve issues early in the development process, saving time and resources in the long run.

**What You Need to Do:**
As a key stakeholder, your support is vital. Please take a moment to familiarize yourself with this integration. If you have any questions, concerns, or suggestions, do not hesitate to reach out to our team at [Email Address] or [Phone Number]. We value your input and are here to assist you throughout this transition.

**Next Steps:**
In the coming weeks, our team will provide additional resources and training to ensure a smooth integration process. We will keep you updated on the timeline and provide detailed instructions on how to use SonarQube's features within Jenkins.

Thank you for your commitment to delivering high-quality software, and we look forward to working together to make this integration a success.

Best regards,
[Your Name]
[Your Title]
[Your Company]
[Contact Information]

Feel free to customize this template to suit your specific needs and add any additional details or links that may be relevant to your integration process.
